<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TPal1">
<l>katiravaṉ kuṇaticaic cikaramvan taṇaintāṉ kaṉaviru ḷakaṉṟatu kālaiyam poḻutāy</l>
<l>matuvirin toḻukiṉa māmala rellām vāṉava raracarkaḷ vantuvan tīṇṭi</l>
<l>yetirticai niṟaintaṉa rivaroṭum pukunta viruṅkaḷiṟ ṟīṭṭamum piṭiyoṭu muracu</l>
<l>matirtali lalaikaṭal pōṉṟuḷa teṅku maraṅkattam māpaḷḷi yeḻuntaru ḷāyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The Sun has come and embraced the mountain top in the eastern direction.</l>
<l>The dense darkness has vanished. As the beautiful morning [dawned],</l>
<l>all the big flowers have unfolded and spilled honey;</l>
<l>celestials [and] kings have come one after the other, gathered together,</l>
<l>and pervaded the opposite direction;</l>
<l>With the resounding of the drums and of the parades of dark bull elephants</l>
<l>along with [their] cows that entered with all these people,</l>
<l>[the place] is like the heaving sea everywhere.</l>
<l>O Lord of Raṅgam, do grace to wake up from sleep!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
